器物有金、银骆驼，金舞袖俑，镶嵌琉璃的铜扁壶等，另有一件小型铜俑，跽姿状，头戴冠，双手捧物，表情肃穆。 据了解，从 2013 年开始，秦陵博物院对这座陪葬墓进行了持续性发掘。考古专家表示，墓主的地位很高，身份尊贵。新出土的大量珍贵文物包括三个车马陪葬坑、 15 个一组的编钟，许许多多的小型乐舞百戏、动物等形象的金银铜俑，都显示出了贵族的奢华生活。考古新发现！秦始皇陵陪葬墓新出土大量珍贵文物 - 西部网（陕西新闻网）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-caa52d3e0f0d5e618b0eca0cc20f4df8_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "17 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/512704654"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5bWCtqq22IE8EAMaCDc2MjE2MTE3ILvCqY8GMAI43gJAHnIJNTEyNzA0NjU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1642863721.3184855", "card_id": "Q_511582697", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 143}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "暗恋三年的人，失联两年还是忘不掉怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "17 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/511582697"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5bWCtqq22IE8EAMaCDc1OTY2NjEyIK6eho8GMAE4rwFAH3IJNTExNTgyNjk3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1642863721.318749", "card_id": "Q_510904334", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 130}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "不合群意味着什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "17 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/510904334"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5bWCtqq22IE8EAMaCDc1ODE1OTM4INv88I4GMAI43QFAIHIJNTEwOTA0MzM0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1642863721.3190022", "card_id": "Q_498916556", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 77}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "什么才是真正努力学习?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "感觉自己总是在假装努力，不知道什么是真正的努力，连我身边的人都说我在假装努力所以什么是真正的努力"}, "i